的原则、模式和实践是这么理解的。首先原则就是理论嘛，模式是由理论到实践的一个中间产物，实践是落地的时候要动手干的事情。\n对应到 DDD 中，原则是实体、值对象这些定义的概念，模式包括代码层面的设计模式和系统层面的架构模式，比如工厂模式、洋葱架构等。实践指的是指来一场事件风暴。实践包括事件风暴、包结构的划分、画 UML等事情。理论指导实践，模式更好的辅助实践的落地。\n我的理解对吗？","like_count":0,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1288110,"avatar":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/VBLEAcychgbs5CicUczSYcibicoicZmyk1JHHFiae94KuvVsibAKtcQAvnOPWp0C4yvia8mzvQAORiazjWSoc1XQ9QkLrQ/132","nickname":"钟敬","note":"","ucode":"20B3D31A2C8C86","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":607539,"discussion_content":"DDD的原则指的是：围绕模型来开发，注重概念一致，业务和开发的协作等等。实体、值对象等，在DDD里算模式（看一下《DDD》原书，标题里有“模式”两个字的都是模式）。对实践的理解没问题。","likes_number":1,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1677931841,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"广东","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":364589,"user_name":"楚天乐","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1777651,"ip_address":"北京","ucode":"320FE64B092196","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1b/1f/f3/ea603815.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1671170683,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":132734,"content":"加油，希望课程对你有启发～","user_name":"编辑回复","user_name_real":"编辑","uid":1501385,"ctime":1671324813,"ip_address":"北京","comment_id":364589,"utype":2}],"discussion_count":2,"race_medal":0,"score":3,"product_id":100311801,"comment_content":"归根结底写代码不能只思考技术，业务加技术二合一才能练成ddd","like_count":0,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1501385,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/e8/c9/59bcd490.jpg","nickname":"听水的湖","note":"","ucode":"B1759F90165D81","race_medal":0,"user_type":8,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussio